 D A T A B A S E
- - - - - - - - - 

This database contains known computer scientist.
You can add new scientists, viwe, sort and/or
search for a scientist in the database.

Select:
1) to input new data.
	Select:
	1) to input new computer scientist.
		Name of the scientist: string
			Error :Invalid input ":" (lúppa til baka í 1)1)name)
		Select gender:
		1) for female
	 	2) for male       
		Selection: int
			Error :Invalid input ". Please select 1 or 2:" (lúppa til baka í 1)1)gender) (vantar)
		Year of birth: int (1800-2015)
			Error :Invalid input ". Please select valid year on the format YYYY: " (lúppa til baka í 1)1)bYear)
		Is the scientist still alive? (y/n): char
			y -> 1)1)add another...
			n -> Year of death
			Error :Invalid input ":" (lúppa til baka í 1)1)is ... alive?)
		Year of death: int (1800-2015)
			Error :Invalid input ". Please select valid year on the format YYYY: " (lúppa til baka í 1)1)dYear)

		Add another scientist? (y/n): char 
			y -> 1)1)name
			n -> upphafsvalmynd
			Error :Invalid input ". Please select y or n: " (lúppa til baka í 1)1) Add another ...)

	2) to input new computer.
		Name of the computer: string
			Error :Invalid input ":" (lúppa til baka í 1)2) Name)			
		Select make:
		1) Electronic 
		2) Mechanical
		3) Transistor  
		Selection: char
			Error :Invalid input ". Please select 1,2 or 3: " (lúppa til baka í 1)2) Make)
		Was the computer ever build? (y/n): char
			y -> continu to year build
			n -> 1)2) Add another?
			Error :Invalid input ". Please select y or n: " (lúppa til baka í 1)2) Was..build?)
		Year build: int (1800-2015)
			Error :Invalid input ". Please select valid year on the format YYYY: " (lúppa til baka í 1)2) Was..build?)
		Add another computer (y/n): char
			y -> 1)2)name
			n -> upphafsvalmynd
			Error :Invalid input ". Please select y or n: " (lúppa til baka í 1)1) Add another ...)
	3) to connect scientist and computer.
		Select:
		1) connect scientist to computer.
			Name of scientist: string
				Scientist not found in database. Try again? (y/n):" 
					y -> (lúppa til baka 1)3)1)
					n -> upphafsvalmynd
					Error :Invalid input ":" (lúppa til baka 1)3)1)
				Scientist found please select computer to connect to:  string
					Connection between "Name of scientist" and "name computer" successfully added.
					Add another connections to "Name of scientist"? (y/n): 
						y -> lúppa í 1)3)1) scientist ... scientist.
						n -> upphafsvalmynd
						Error :Invalid input ":" (lúppa til baka 1)3)1 Scientist ... to)
					Computer not found in database. Try again? (y/n):" 
						y -> (lúppa til baka 1)3)1 Scientist ... to)
						n -> upphafsvalmynd
						Error :Invalid input ". Please select y or n: " (lúppa til baka 1)3)1) computer... database)
				Sleppi error hér dugar að hafa scientist not found.	

			Add another connections? (y/n): char
				y -> 1)3)1)
				n -> upphafsvalmynd
				Error :Invalid input ". Please select y or n: " (lúppa til baka í 1)3)1) Add another ...)		
		2) connect computer to scientist.
			Name of computer: string
				Computer not found in database. Try again? (y/n):" 
					y -> (lúppa til baka 1)3)2)
					n -> upphafsvalmynd
					Error :Invalid input ":" (lúppa til baka 1)3)2)
				Computer found please select scientist to connect to:  string
					Connection between "Name of computer" and "name of scientist" successfully added.
					Add another connections to "Name of computer(y/n): 
						y -> (lúppa í 1)3)2) Computer... to)
						n -> upphafsvalmynd
					"Scientist not found in database. Try again? (y/n):" 
						y -> (lúppa til baka 1)3)2 Computer...  to)
						n -> upphafsvalmynd
						Error :Invalid input ". Please select y or n: " (lúppa til baka 1)3)2) computer... database)
				Sleppi error hér dugar að hafa computer not found.	

			Add another connections? (y/n): char
				y -> 1)3)2)
				n -> upphafsvalmynd
				Error :Invalid input ". Please select y or n: " (lúppa til baka í 1)3)2) Add another ...)
		Selection: char
		Error :Invalid input". Please select 1 or 2: " (lúppa til baka)
2) to search in the existing database.
	1) to search for scientist
		1) by name. <tekur við list<Scientist> og prentar út>
			"Search again? (y/n): " char
				y -> (loop 2))
				n -> (upphafsvalmynd)
				Error :Invalid input ". Please select y or n: " (lúppa til baka 2)1)1))
			"Scientist not found do you want to search again? (y/n):" 
				y -> (loop 2))
				n -> (upphafsvalmynd)
				Error :Invalid input ". Please select y or n: " (lúppa til baka 2)1)1)))
		2) by gender. <tekur við list<Scientist> og prentar út>
			"Search again? (y/n): " char
				y -> (loop 2))
				n -> (upphafsvalmynd)
				Error :Invalid input ". Please select y or n: " (lúppa til baka 2)1)2))
			"Scientist not found do you want to search again? (y/n):" 
				y -> (loop 2))
				n -> (upphafsvalmynd)
				Error :Invalid input ". Please select y or n: " (lúppa til baka 2)1)2)))
		3) by year of birth <tekur við list<Scientist> og prentar út>
			"Search again? (y/n): " char
				y -> (loop 2))
				n -> (upphafsvalmynd)
				Error :Invalid input ". Please select y or n: " (lúppa til baka 2)1)2))
			"Scientist not found do you want to search again? (y/n):" 
				y -> (loop 2))
				n -> (upphafsvalmynd)
				Error :Invalid input ". Please select y or n: " (lúppa til baka 2)1)2)))
		4) by year of death <tekur við list<Scientist> og prentar út>
			"Search again? (y/n): " char
				y -> (loop 2))
				n -> (upphafsvalmynd)
				Error :Invalid input ". Please select y or n: " (lúppa til baka 2)1)2))
			"Scientist not found do you want to search again? (y/n):" 
				y -> (loop 2))
				n -> (upphafsvalmynd)
				Error :Invalid input ". Please select y or n: " (lúppa til baka 2)1)2)))
	2) to search for computer.
		1) by name <tekur við list<Computer> og prentar út>
			"Search again? (y/n): " char
				y -> (loop 2))
				n -> (upphafsvalmynd)
				Error :Invalid input ". Please select y or n: " (lúppa til baka 2)2)1))
			"Scientist not found do you want to search again? (y/n):" 
				y -> (loop 2))
				n -> (upphafsvalmynd)
				Error :Invalid input ". Please select y or n: " (lúppa til baka 2)2)1)))
		2) by year build <tekur við list<Computer> og prentar út>
			"Search again? (y/n): " char
				y -> (loop 2))
				n -> (upphafsvalmynd)
				Error :Invalid input ". Please select y or n: " (lúppa til baka 2)2)1))
			"Scientist not found do you want to search again? (y/n):" 
				y -> (loop 2))
				n -> (upphafsvalmynd)
				Error :Invalid input ". Please select y or n: " (lúppa til baka 2)2)1)))
		3) by <tekur við list<Computer> og prentar út>
			"Search again? (y/n): " char
				y -> (loop 2))
				n -> (upphafsvalmynd)
				Error :Invalid input ". Please select y or n: " (lúppa til baka 2)2)1))
			"Scientist not found do you want to search again? (y/n):" 
				y -> (loop 2))
